"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-30-CGTN-talks-to-Olympic-bidding-organizing-expert-Laszlo-Vajda-1vEqC4PsyCQ-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  Since 1998, Laszlo Vajda has helped multiple countries with bidding for the Olympics and also organizing\\u00a0them, including the 2008 Beijing Summer Games and 2022 Beijing Winter Games. Vajda, a professor at Capital University of Physical Education, also serves as the secretary of International Teqball Federation. He talks about his experience across different Olympic Games and how he is trying to push Teqball to get the recognition of the International Olympic Committee.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"